Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.88,Default,F,0,0,0,,Orders to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.26,Default,F,0,0,0,,Why, on such short notice, Abbot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:10.88,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,It is a direct order from the Holy See.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:15.35,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,It can be said that the heretics \Nhave been sufficiently quelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.99,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,I thank you for your long service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.32,Default,F,0,0,0,,Remnants may yet be hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.67,Default,F,0,0,0,,The people are still unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:27.90,Default,F,0,0,0,,The investigations and sentencing \Nwill take time to conclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:30.98,Default,F,0,0,0,,In the meantime, what will you \Ndo to maintain security?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.74,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,You needn't worry yourself about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:37.47,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,This directive was not addressed \Nto the Holy Iron Chain Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:40.26,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,But to you alone, Lady Farnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.60,Default,F,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.91,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am to abandon my own troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the commander, should abandon our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.14,Default,F,0,0,0,,I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.27,Default,F,0,0,0,,I cannot accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.43,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,As for your current mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:54.91,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,having Vice-Commander Azan lead in \Nyour stead should not be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.95,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, it appears that \Nthis directive comes, in part,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at the wish of Lord Vandimion, your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.27,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,I ask you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:14.08,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,Though this may be a holy mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:16.16,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,your father does not wish you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:20.05,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,as a woman, to remain long \Nin such a gruesome place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.06,Default,F,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:28.31,Default,Abbot,0,0,0,,House Vandimion funds the majority \Nof relief supplies for these refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.82,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.32,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Please wait, Lady Farnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.45,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:44.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,You told my father, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.57,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:47.09,Default,F,0,0,0,,I know it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:51.25,Default,F,0,0,0,,You report to my family on my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.88,Default,F,0,0,0,,You probably wrote that I am \Njoyously hunting heretics
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,and burning them at the stake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.46,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.32,Default,F,0,0,0,,Was it at my father's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.85,Default,F,0,0,0,,You couldn't deny the master of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.00,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.60,Default,F,0,0,0,,But do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:14.08,Default,F,0,0,0,,You swore your sword to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.14,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am your only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:21.74,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.36,Default,F,0,0,0,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.00,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.00,Default,Dwarf,0,0,0,,I have never met anyone as pathetic as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.36,Default,Dwarf,0,0,0,,You blabbed everything before I \Ncould take a single fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.01,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:51.36,Default,Dwarf,0,0,0,,Having sold out your friend, \Nenjoy your last night alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.49,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Sorry... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.90,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Please forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.79,Title,Sign 0308,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,256)}Blood Flow of the Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.51,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Well done, Lady Farnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.07,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,It would not be an exaggeration to say
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.69,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,that we have captured nearly \Nall of the heretics at Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:51.56,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Your reputation as the Holy Iron Chain \NKnights' commander is well deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.56,Default,F,0,0,0,,No, it is thanks to God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:58.11,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,By the way, your report indicates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:04.15,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,that your men encountered several anomalies \Nwhile raiding the heretics' lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:10.47,Default,F,0,0,0,,The cave was full of arcane drugs \Nand incense that the heretics use
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,during their rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:16.55,Default,F,0,0,0,,I believe they may have triggered \Na mass hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.04,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,According to the report,\Nthere is one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:26.04,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,The Black Swordsman, previously sought \Nby your knights, appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.09,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Hmm, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.87,Default,Dwarf,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:34.85,Default,F,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.78,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.81,Default,F,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:43.20,Default,F,0,0,0,,It's just, when the Black\NSwordsman appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.50,Default,F,0,0,0,,he seemed to be trying to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.47,Default,Heretics,0,0,0,,Witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.57,Default,Heretics,0,0,0,,Please save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.11,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Reporting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.87,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,The heretics' confessions indicate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.87,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,that the girl is their priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.24,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Or, perhaps, the very object of their faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:04.00,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,The priestess of heretics, with ties \Nto the Black Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.53,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:18.23,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,This is a witch's brand indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:24.82,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Evidently, we must take special \Ncare in investigating this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.71,Default,P,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:04.98,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Casca...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.48,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.20,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,You two, stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.57,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I know you want to hurry, but if \Nyou cause a commotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.35,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,you'll lose your chance to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.61,Default,Trash,0,0,0,,Huh? I haven't seen you around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.20,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I got a personal summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.92,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Sorry, but would you take a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.01,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm here for Jerome, of the \NHoly Iron Chain Knights—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.87,Default,Trash,0,0,0,,Huh? Did someone just pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.91,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm sure you imagined it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.70,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.36,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Wh-What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.48,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.58,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Stay back, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.16,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.38,Default - Apostle,Spirits,0,0,0,,I hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.38,Default - Apostle,Spirits,0,0,0,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.38,Default - Apostle,Spirits,0,0,0,,I'm cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.91,Default,Torturer,0,0,0,,M-Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.64,Default,Torturer,0,0,0,,They eat humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.06,Default,Heretics,0,0,0,,Don't leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.65,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Please hurry, Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.65,Default,F,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.65,Default,F,0,0,0,,Father Mozgus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.65,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Father Mozgus, we must retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.11,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Impertinent witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.47,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,The front entrance is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.41,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Let's escape to the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.24,Default,P,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.28,Default,P,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.74,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.36,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,For now, let us ascend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.26,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,I shall explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.69,Default,F,0,0,0,,Y-You—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.69,Default,G,0,0,0,,Where is my companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.20,Default,F,0,0,0,,Then you did come here for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.72,Default,G,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.91,Default,F,0,0,0,,Th-That girl is in the cellar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the torture chamber...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.21,Default,G,0,0,0,,The torture chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.04,Default,G,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.21,Default,F,0,0,0,,I-It's no use. Even if you go there now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.25,Default,F,0,0,0,,In the cellar, there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.72,Default,F,0,0,0,,There are so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.93,Default,G,0,0,0,,Hey! Get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.66,Default,F,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.19,Default,F,0,0,0,,They shouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.34,Default,F,0,0,0,,They can't exist. Not those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.12,Default,G,0,0,0,,Take me to that torture chamber of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.21,Default,F,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.73,Default,F,0,0,0,,Who would go there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.86,Default,G,0,0,0,,Sorry, but hurry it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.03,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'm about to snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.81,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm so useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.65,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm a worthless human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.79,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Only one more night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.77,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Even now, I'm only worried about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.89,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Because of me, by now, Elaine must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:30.92,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.02,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I don't want to die—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.73,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.58,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Up! Run up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:38.93,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,What about the prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.75,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Who cares? Abandon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.03,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.78,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,U-Um, did...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.42,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:48.98,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.28,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.34,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.56,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,It's coming from below?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.18,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Guards! Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.03,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.01,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Please, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.02,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.69,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.46,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.44,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.32,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,The emotional reunion will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.57,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.57,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Hey, now! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.60,Default,Heretics,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.61,Default,Heretics,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.80,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,It's the plan. It's a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.83,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,We'll use them as bait, and escape \Nwhile they distract the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:32.08,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Hey, I may not look it, but I \Nam a heretic hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.15,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,You're saying that, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.84,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,You're an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.91,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Damned brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.42,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Sorry, Jerome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.11,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to involve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.59,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Honestly, I've reached\Nthe end of my rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.31,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,But I guess it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.88,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,I didn't like the mission, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.93,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,And this gives me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.60,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Ruining my future over a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.73,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,may be fitting for a prodigal son like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.38,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Jerome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.24,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,All right. With that decided, \Nlet's get out of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.99,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Sorry, we have one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.48,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Nina, where's Elaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.75,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,d-don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.81,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,She's probably in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:19.51,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone. This is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:25.88,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.99,Default,F,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:51.79,Default,F,0,0,0,,Only a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.13,Default,F,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.48,Default,F,0,0,0,,That thing did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.06,Default,G,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.94,Default,G,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.56,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,Trying to get heavy armor \Nand run down the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.59,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,I sneaked in here to save Casca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.07,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,But those things came out of \Nthe woodwork in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.29,Default,G,0,0,0,,Where is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.52,Default,G,0,0,0,,Where is Casca?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.32,Default,P,0,0,0,,Casca was swallowed up by them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.24,Default,P,0,0,0,,Oh, but something didn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.76,Default,P,0,0,0,,Everyone else melted right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.45,Default,P,0,0,0,,but Casca didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.09,Default,P,0,0,0,,Even though she was swallowed, \NI could still sense her presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.61,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.26,Default,P,0,0,0,,I think she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.96,Default,P,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.71,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.34,Default,P,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.17,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.89,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:52.27,Default,G,0,0,0,,Hey, you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.04,Default,F,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.11,Default,F,0,0,0,,I'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.25,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Please stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.00,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,The doors will give way soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.51,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,There is nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:35.27,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,This is our faith's moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.00,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,We do not pray to God for salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.41,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Faith requires everything from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:46.78,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Repent, evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:52.53,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I have found that faith means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.54,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.39,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Master, draw back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:05.14,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,No matter what may challenge me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.50,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.31,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I need to go downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.35,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Escaping is the priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.36,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Elaine, I hope you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.58,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.45,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,If I remember right, the chapel's ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.18,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Those doors are pretty thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.71,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Ideal for holing up in—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.50,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.68,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:46.68,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.49,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.71,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.73,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I have witnessed a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.82,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,This is God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.19,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I am to guide the people with this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.32,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Elaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.74,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,That's Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.13,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Hey, square-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.74,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Hand over that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.52,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,That will not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.54,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,This witch is the origin of the \Nevil that festers in Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.57,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I am destined to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:32.01,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,God's victory to the people, by burning \Nthis witch at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.75,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,What witch are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.37,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,You guys look tons more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.01,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Guess we have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.29,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:42.91,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,You seek to interfere with my sacred duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:48.61,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,My disciples have no mercy \Ntoward enemies of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:00.66,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Hey, those are above my pay grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:04.92,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.25,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,M-Mister, another attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.51,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,The next one's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.93,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,It's fine! Pull them up, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.87,Default,P,0,0,0,,Here, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.44,Default,P,0,0,0,,The presence is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.20,Default,F,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.71,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.45,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.73,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,So heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.86,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,This is how heavy Luca is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:50.34,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm holding Luca's life in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:56.72,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Right now, all that she is rests in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.80,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,If I were to let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.22,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Jerome, take care of Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:04.98,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.81,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Hurry! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:09.35,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.60,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.85,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:15.95,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.99,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.00,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,Is it Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.98,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.61,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I-It flew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.98,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.53,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.14,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:09.78,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Um, you're Death... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.17,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Girl, why did you choose to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.62,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.67,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm not that noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.35,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Look, that tower is really tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.55,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,But it has a couple layers, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.68,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have slammed into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.78,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I thought I could maybe get \Naway with a broken leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.69,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,as long as the roofs were wooden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:36.23,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Well, now that I think about it, \Nit was pretty reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.38,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I thought it was the only choice, \Nso everyone could live, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.20,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,But I guess it didn't work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.94,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I got lucky and was spared pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:49.14,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,but this doesn't really feel like Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.60,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.32,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,This is a resting place for the dead, \Nat the foot of that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.21,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.45,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean I'm still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.09,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.79,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,If you wish to stay so, do not move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.78,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.10,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:18.19,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,So you are the famed Black Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.22,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I do not know what you seek to accomplish,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.98,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,but I cannot let you have this witch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.41,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,in the name of God's justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:38.98,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Fool, you seek to rebel against God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:43.05,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I will have you atone with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.46,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,An Apostle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.79,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,No, it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.48,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,My brand senses something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.77,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,They'll be formidable foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.23,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,And seven of them, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.75,Default,P,0,0,0,,Guts, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.70,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.46,Default,P,0,0,0,,It was only possible with my assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.45,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Brat, you've got something \Nstrange on your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.49,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,When did they...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.72,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I can't avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.97,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:20.54,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Just one more step.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:01.50,Title,Sign 2404,0,0,0,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:05.50,EndInsert,Sign 2404,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.59,EndInsert,Sign 2408,0,0,0,,Screams?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,EndInsert,Sign 2412,0,0,0,,It begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:17.56,EndInsert,Sign 2416,0,0,0,,Elven Lethal Head-Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:21.56,EndInsert,Sign 2420,0,0,0,,We desire only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:27.70,Title2,Sign 2425,0,0,0,,Next Episode \NHell's Angels
